General.Name: AIQ Ltd
General.Description: AIQ Limited, through its subsidiaries, designs and develops software solutions. The company offers messaging solution for business customers and an AI-powered online shopping platform. It is also involved in the website development business. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Grand Cayman, the Cayman Islands.
